abstract: >
  Remem is an AI-native work reuse engine that reduces latency and inference
  cost in Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG), AI agent, and LLM applications
  by intelligently reusing previous executions through semantic similarity and
  policy-aware decision making.

keywords:
  - AI Infrastructure
